OL,3,CStove manufacturer fined #200,000
OL,4,Cafter employee loses leg
OL,6,FHSE said a similar incident had
OL,7,Fhappened in November 2021, yet a safe
OL,8,Fsystem of work had not been introduced.
OL,10,FThe regulator for workplace health and
OL,11,Fsafety said if appropriate changes
OL,12,Fbeen made following the earlier
OL,13,Fincident, this life-changing injury
OL,14,Fcould have been prevented.
OL,16,FA J Wells & Sons Ltd pleaded guilty to
OL,17,Fbreaching Section 2(1) of the Health
OL,18,Fand Safety at Work etc. Act 1974.
