OL,4,Cafter employee loses leg
OL,6,FThe company was fined #200,000 and
OL,7,Fordered to pay #9,056 in prosecution
OL,8,Fcosts at Isle of Wight Magistrates'.
OL,10,FHSE inspector Nicola Pinckney said:
OL,11,F"This is a particularly unfortunate
OL,12,Fcase as lessons from a previous
OL,13,Fsimilar incident had not been learnt.
OL,15,F"This young man will be affected by
OL,16,Fthis accident for the rest of his life
OL,17,Fand has to suffer the consequences of
OL,18,Fthe company's failings.
